title: Ranked START ALREADY
body:
WHY ISNT RANKED UP? 

I've been closing in and out of my client to try and update and see whether or not ranked is up, just checking if my client is glitching etc, I live in Brisbane, and at the moment its roughly 7:30am, ranked still isn't up. What the fuck...{{item:3070}}

replies.body:
Server shut down @ 3am, down for around 6 hours. Should have gone up around 9am.

Try it now.
